Basinger (eds.), Burlington, VT: Ashgate Publishing Company, pp.
75&ndash; 84.</li>

<li>&ndash;&ndash;&ndash;, 2012, <em>On Religious Diversity</em>,
Oxford: Oxford University Press.</li>

<li>Pittard, John, 2020, <em>Disagreement, Deference, and Religious
Commitment</em>, Oxford: Oxford University Press.</li>

<li>Potter, Dennis, 2013, &ldquo;Religious Disagreement: Internal and
External&rdquo;, <em>International Journal for the Philosophy of
Religion</em>, 74: 21&ndash;31.</li>

<li>Quinn, Philip, 2005b, &ldquo;Religious Diversity: Familiar
Problems, Novel Opportunities&rdquo;, in <em>The Oxford Handbook of
